| HasEmbeddingsFilter | Quickly identify sources needing embedding generation |
| Resource/Embedded counts | Track progress on embedding pipeline |
| Date first published field | Sort/filter resources by publication date |
| Date field in admin form | Edit publication dates directly |

### For End Users (Search/Dashboard)

| Change | Benefit |
|--------|---------|
| Query AI on dashboard | Ask questions without leaving homepage |
| Scrollable filter panel | Access all filters without scrolling page |
| Dropdown filters | Less visual clutter, same functionality |
